# its all mona helpfull cheatsheet

- set mona working folder
!mona config -set workingfolder C:\logs\%p

- pattern create (membuat jumlah pattern)
!mona pc jumlah_pattern

- deteksi offset
!mona findmsp valueOffset (yang di EIP eg: 0x181818181818)
!mona pattern_offset valueOffset (eg: 0x181818181818)

- cek seluruh modules (vulnerable modules)
!mona modules

- finding jmp esp modules
!mona find -s "\xff\xe4" -m namamodules

- generate badchars
!mona bytearray

- compare badchars
!mona compare -f C:\path-to-working-direktori\bytearray.bin -a badchars-program

